headline: Prologis to Announce Fourth Quarter 2024 Results January 21st
summary: Prologis, Inc. (NYSE: PLD), the global leader in logistics real estate, will host a webcast and conference call with senior management to discuss fourth quarter results, current market conditions and future outlook on Tuesday, January 21, 2025, at 9:00 a.m. PT/12:00 p.m. ET.

headline: Palantir’s high valuation paints a stark picture of the S&P 500’s priciest picks
summary: You have probably seen warnings that after two years of double-digit gains for the S 500, stocks are getting pricey. Then again, you find warnings that the sky is about to fall down every day in the financial media.
